msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "问候管理人并询问关于宇航机器人的事。"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:57728
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“是吗。舰长，你知道得比你应该知道的多。是的，我们确实开发过超级飞船，但该项目的资金已被切断，所有开发均已冻结。反叛军知道后，当然想夺取宇航机器人来对抗联邦。这艘飞船安装了特殊的先进AI、重力引擎，其工作原理……总之你也不会懂的……”"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:57730
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "表示同意。毕竟你确实不精通引擎的工作原理。"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:57732
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“所以，反叛军向我们承诺了资金、防范海盗的保护、定期的粮食补给和必要设备。作为交换，我们必须为他们完成飞船的工作。我们当然同意了。因为现在我们终于能完成多年来的项目了。不幸还是幸运的是，我们没来得及给它装上独特的佐尔坦护盾，因为反叛军催得很紧，设定了严苛的工作截止日期。”"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:57734
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续听下去……"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:57736
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "就在这时，管理人注意到了你身后的摩根。“呵，瞧瞧那是谁。你好啊，摩根。你还是决定要摧毁我们伟大的项目吗？你都告诉这个舰长什么了？”"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:57738
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "亲自回答。"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:57740
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "“教授，您对自我复制模块只字未提。难道您不觉得这台机器非常危险吗？尤其是在叛军手中。”"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:57742
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "列别丁斯基开始发火了……"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:57744
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "“不，我不觉得，船长！你根本不懂！这是杰作！是科学奇迹！再说，你有什么资格评判这台机器的行为？”"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:57746
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "“我为什么没有资格？毕竟，我的使命是将重要情报送达联邦基地，这关系到反抗叛军战争的胜负以及银河系所有种族的未来。”"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:57748
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "“船长，你太傲慢也太愚蠢了！更何况你们船上还有一名逃犯。我们将连同你们的船一起摧毁。开火！”"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:57753
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "“也许我确实没资格评判。但您似乎忘了机器人三定律！这是创造机器人时最该记住的东西！”"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:57755
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“你说得对，船长。我祖父菲尔·法恩斯沃思常说，科学家与疯狂之间只隔着基本准则。如果你还没销毁那个机器人，我自己来！幸运的是，我还没疯到忘记安装强制自毁模块。谢谢你点醒我，作为感谢，请允许我在你们的船上安装我们的佐尔坦护盾。”"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:57757
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "感谢教授，并开始与空间站对接。"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:57759
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "在安装佐尔坦护盾模块时，你和船员们在当地酒吧喝了一杯，欣赏着黑洞缓慢吞噬几颗明亮恒星的壮观景象。不久后，你们回到船上，准备继续航行。"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:57770
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "让摩根回答。"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:57772
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "“列别丁斯基，你就是个疯老头！这种机器根本就不该存在！否则我们都要为这个‘伟大的项目’付出代价！”"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:57774
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"BLACK_ZOLTAN_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
